column5: i haven't posted any reports this season, so I wanted to share one or two lunge pics from this fall.  Having a blast in the cold water.  this one pulled drag like heavy log, what a solid fish!     And this one was not very long, but what a girth all the way through.    Lets get a few more before ice up!
I want to hook into whatever it was that tried to take a bite out of the first one!! Nice fish there!
Two very nice Lunge! That second one is thick!
Two really decent ski's there, good job  Joey
One hundred percent sure that those are not fish. They are slobby giants that can, in one bite, demolish a large city.  Pure Fil'th  Thanks for posting man. I always check you out on your site.
Where did you score those, they are huge!
Good stuff Loic now get out there...you still have 4 weeks to go.
Awesome Muskies Loic!!!.....I miss your reports bud!...just like Roy said, we almost have 4 weeks left so looking forward to seeing a few more giants from you!....
Those are some amazing fish. Thanks for posting.
wow amazing fish! Those are some real beauts ya got there! Thanks fo for sharing
Dang they are a couple nice looking slobs congratz
